channel.title: SEEKER FINDER
channel.description: After decades of silent seclusion, SEEKER FINDER now shares his vast wealth of experience with the spirit-beings that inhabit our rapidly deteriorating world, and the hope and help they bring for our redemption and recovery. Though he remains for the most part unknown, he has lived a life in the spirit world unlike any since the days of the Apostles. His life story, the things he has witnessed, the miracles he has participated in --- will simply, blow your mind. All Audio by SEEKER FINDER recorded and processed at IF Studios by owner/sound engineer & publisher Rick Denny. All Music employed in this PodCast by Composer - IF.
